    dc:description "FIGURE 7. A–B, Ficomila carolae Lotfalizadeh & Rasplus sp. n., mesosoma in ventral view and lateroventral views, respectively. C–D, S. (Ficorytoma) delvarei Lotfalizadeh & Rasplus sp. n., mesosoma in ventral view and lateroventral views, respectively. Arrow in B and D points to ring-like process and areolation of mesodiscrimen, respectively." ;
